latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Presenting GROWLONG RICE Hair Care Range. 

Take the 3 Step Growlong Challenge for long, shiny and healthy hair. 

STEP 1: AEGTE GROWLONG RICE HAIR OIL

Massage the oil from root to top of the hair. Detangle the hair using wide-tooth comb to ensure even distribution all over the hair. 

STEP 2: AEGTE GROWLONG RICE HAIR SHAMPOO

Wet your hair, apply the shampoo on the scalp and massage it nicely to cleanse the oil. 

Rinse off your hair with normal water.

STEP 3: AEGTE GROWLONG RICE HAIR CONDITIONER 

After rinsing the shampoo, apply the conditioner on the hair including ends. Leave it for a few minutes.

Rinse off with normal water, let your hair dry naturally.

The range is made of benefits of Fermented Rice Water, Banana, Rosemary extract and Flaxseeds. 

Effective for men and women both and is suitable for all hair types. 

Sulphate & Paraben free
